{"tid":2449891,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國女性遭警員綁架殺害 國會審議限制示威及集會自由","createTime":"2021-03-17T04:16:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T05:19:33.000Z","uid":27458,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1d0afe4800b6e7c73b1411b419146341b35e78d4","tid":2449891,"uid":27458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T04:16:30.000Z","msg":"英國倫敦有夜歸女遭警員綁架殺害的案件持續發酵，更引申到警權、限制示威自由的關注。當地連續三日有示威悼念遇害身亡的33歲女子埃弗拉德（Sarah Everard），而期間警方武力驅散哀悼者的手法受到全國譴責，周一是英國《警察、罪案、判罪與法庭法案》於國會審議的日子，過千人於國會外示威，除抗議警暴以及關注女性在英國的人身安全問題外，示威者認為法案賦予警方更大權力限制示威自由...<br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n...大批民眾於上周六在埃弗拉德生前最後現身的克拉法姆公園（Clapham Common）悼念、獻上鮮花和蠟燭，英國威廉王子之妻凱特亦有現身。惟當晚警方以違反防疫為由，驅散民眾時爆發警民衝突，最終警方稱當晚有4人被捕...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210317/S6QGLB42EJHUDDQXDAE6QJAE3Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210317%2FS6QGLB42EJHUDDQXDAE6QJAE3Q%2F&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixSNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=c93c1acd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210317%2FS6QGLB42EJHUDDQXDAE6QJAE3Q%2F&h=7466a744\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210317/S6QGLB42EJHUDDQXDAE6QJAE3Q/</a>"},{"pid":"2624b8af4df2444c107dedb4d3d9a164b60621c1","tid":2449891,"uid":27458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T04:24:49.000Z","msg":"狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb0839ed55a6261231d59e8233ed4846d0cb6c7e","tid":2449891,"uid":199826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T05:19:33.000Z","msg":"英國個啲唔係狗"}]}